{"tid":1457323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲大家聽日旅客裝束，和理非去發夢（操各國語言更佳）","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:27:32.000Z","uid":67306,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"612205fa4a1e60758c8a2a66c006d66a7f5c60e8","tid":1457323,"uid":67306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"琴晚大家有幾嬲，今日係機場已經見到<br />\n作為見面禮，已經令到狗隻自關機場<br />\n相信國際旅客，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">應該從來無見過香港機場落哂閘既盛況，其實是一種另類成功</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n一直以來，大家都俾黑衫、頭盔、盾牌限制住，其實係咪應該要變一變？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點解佔領機場咁惡？</span></span></strong><br />\n因為果度有旅客、有公司客，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最重要仲有偉大祖國的同胞</strong></span></span><br />\n（據淋病的吹奏，我地<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港做好多好多自由行生意</span></span></ins></strong>，無左香港會<strong><ins><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">陸沉</span></span></ins></strong> ga）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>如果我地著一般遊客衫，拎住個香港人最憎既旅行喼、帶埋 passport、帶埋文宣資料<br />\n入到去仲要操流利普通話、日文、韓文、法文........邊個分到我地係咪遊客？</ins></span></ins></strong><br />\n邊個夠膽驅散我地？<br />\n犬隻扮人類惡，因為我地有鮮明制服<br />\n當我地唔著黑衫，我地就係遊客<br />\n但我地有樣野要做，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">派文宣，叫口號<br />\n如果犬隻扮我地，佢地一樣要預備文宣資料</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n如果佢印<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>我地既文宣，即係幫緊我地</ins></strong></span></span>，我地何必捉佢，咪俾佢做下香港人<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>佢印 CCTV 的文宣，我地賭下 30000 幾犬隻，同幾十萬民眾</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><ins>有起事上黎，旁邊係人類多定犬隻多</ins></strong></span>，邊個救到佢地？<br />\n大家如果發現 spy，記得剋制自己怒火<br />\n護送佢入廁所慢慢同佢抹屎抹尿，唔好傷到人地丫<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，大家今次無講錯，我地真係可以除低口罩相見<br />\n水炮車就黎出，呢個都係我地最後一戰<br />\n如果大家信任我地咁耐既運動，果幾十萬人唔係吹水唔係俾錢的<br />\n呢個將會係我地既重要一戰，如果連露一露面大家都唔想<br />\n民主、自由、平等實在唔係我地香港人應該擁有的東西<br />\n國際都會，就係世界知名既國際機場解決<br />\n大家沖涼換衫，聽日見！（定機場永遠唔開......=P）"},{"pid":"ab4969dc21a17ad90cdf4cbef69d8d89d4e3c89b","tid":1457323,"uid":244588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"英雄所見略同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為社大fm我諗住攞gip玩全港最大型ocamp<br />\n咩色衫都可以着"},{"pid":"b1c01019a7192d05cfeb2da5037289cc215afd03","tid":1457323,"uid":67306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:42:49.000Z","msg":"自推 10 次<br />\n10"},{"pid":"fd03d787590be0b9dde13a91c603241c4e17caef","tid":1457323,"uid":124133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7ef555347ff93b51e4861983dcc1bc26e70d00","tid":1457323,"uid":67306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:15:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"345728feb650b4d011b5250d84f88226775d5689","tid":1457323,"uid":67306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7823ce75d02678d8bef01ce4de28b8afe9fb5c2","tid":1457323,"uid":1142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"但一定要帶gear"},{"pid":"d631b2e02c288e9ed8fc659fb001f637e9f76ab5","tid":1457323,"uid":244588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:01:00.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ab55d11c157f7f5cf6393ead09cb1fcbf40244","tid":1457323,"uid":67306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:47:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a679d325ec3904a4e92b1571e0e672ac7619be92","tid":1457323,"uid":282677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:51:40.000Z","msg":"帶埋gip旅客裝束"},{"pid":"763f8